<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>JAMU Java — Bientôt en ligne</title>
<meta name="description" content="JAMU Java arrive bientôt. Jamu ancestral et café d'altitude, sourcés directement à Yogyakarta, Indonésie.">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --cream:#FAF8F3;
  --deep:#1A1510;
  --gold:#B8965A;
  --gold-light:#D4B47A;
  --warm:#E8E0D0;
  --muted:#7A6E5F;
  --green:#2D4A3E;
  --font-serif:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;
  --font-sans:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
}
html,body{height:100%}
body{
  background:linear-gradient(150deg,#1A1510 0%,#1F2A22 45%,#1A1510 100%);
  color:var(--cream);
  font-family:var(--font-sans);
  font-weight:300;
  overflow-x:hidden;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  min-height:100vh;
}

/* subtle ambient texture, no images */
.bg-pattern{
  position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;
  opacity:.05;
  background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,var(--gold) 0,var(--gold) 1px,transparent 0,transparent 48px);
}
.bg-glow{
  position:fixed;
  top:-10%;right:-10%;
  width:60vw;height:60vw;
  max-width:700px;max-height:700px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(184,150,90,.18),transparent 70%);
  z-index:0;
  animation:drift 14s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes drift{0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)}50%{transform:translate(-3%,3%)}}

nav{
  position:relative;z-index:10;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:2rem 3rem;
}
.logo{
  font-family:var(--font-serif);
  font-size:1.5rem;
  letter-spacing:.2em;
  color:var(--cream);
}
.logo-sub{
  font-size:.62rem;
  letter-spacing:.25em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);
  opacity:.8;
}

main{
  position:relative;z-index:10;
  flex:1;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  text-align:center;
  padding:2rem 1.5rem;
}

.eyebrow{
  font-size:.68rem;
  letter-spacing:.32em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:2rem;
  opacity:.9;
}

h1{
  font-family:var(--font-serif);
  font-weight:300;
  font-size:clamp(2.8rem,8vw,5.5rem);
  line-height:1.05;
  letter-spacing:.01em;
  margin-bottom:1.8rem;
}
h1 em{
  font-style:italic;
  color:var(--gold-light);
}

.sub{
  font-size:.95rem;
  line-height:1.9;
  color:rgba(250,248,243,.6);
  max-width:480px;
  margin-bottom:3rem;
  letter-spacing:.01em;
}

.divider{
  width:44px;height:1px;
  background:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:3rem;
  opacity:.6;
}

form{
  width:100%;
  max-width:420px;
  margin-bottom:1.2rem;
}
.input-row{
  display:flex;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(250,248,243,.3);
  transition:border-color .3s;
  margin-bottom:1rem;
}
.input-row:focus-within{border-color:var(--gold)}
input[type="email"]{
  background:transparent;
  border:none;
  outline:none;
  color:var(--cream);
  font-size:.92rem;
  font-family:var(--font-sans);
  font-weight:300;
  padding:.9rem .2rem;
  flex:1;
  letter-spacing:.02em;
  min-width:0;
}
input[type="email"]::placeholder{color:rgba(250,248,243,.4)}
.submit-btn{
  background:transparent;
  border:none;
  color:var(--gold);
  cursor:pointer;
  font-size:.7rem;
  letter-spacing:.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:.9rem .4rem;
  transition:color .3s;
  font-family:var(--font-sans);
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.submit-btn:hover{color:var(--gold-light)}
.form-note{
  font-size:.7rem;
  color:rgba(250,248,243,.35);
  letter-spacing:.04em;
}

.confirm{
  display:none;
  font-size:.85rem;
  color:var(--gold-light);
  letter-spacing:.02em;
  padding:.9rem 0;
}
.confirm.visible{display:block}

.socials{
  display:flex;
  gap:1.5rem;
  margin-top:3rem;
}
.social-link{
  font-size:.68rem;
  letter-spacing:.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(250,248,243,.5);
  text-decoration:none;
  border-bottom:1px solid transparent;
  transition:all .3s;
  padding-bottom:.2rem;
}
.social-link:hover{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold)}

footer{
  position:relative;z-index:10;
  text-align:center;
  padding:2rem;
  font-size:.65rem;
  letter-spacing:.1em;
  color:rgba(250,248,243,.25);
}

@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.bg-glow{animation:none}}

@media(max-width:640px){
  nav{padding:1.5rem 1.5rem}
  .input-row{flex-direction:column;border-bottom:none;gap:.8rem}
  input[type="email"]{border:1px solid rgba(250,248,243,.3);padding:.9rem 1rem}
  .submit-btn{border:1px solid var(--gold);text-align:center}
  .socials{flex-direction:column;gap:1rem}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg-pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="bg-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

<nav>
  <div>
    <div class="logo">JAMU Java</div>
    <div class="logo-sub">Boissons de Java · Indonésie</div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>
  <p class="eyebrow">Bientôt à Yogyakarta &amp; chez vous</p>
  <h1>L'âme de Java<br>arrive <em>bientôt.</em></h1>
  <p class="sub">Nous préparons quelque chose qui mérite votre attention : jamu ancestral et café d'altitude, sourcés directement auprès des producteurs de Yogyakarta. Laissez-nous votre email pour être averti dès l'ouverture.</p>
  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <form id="notifyForm">
    <div class="input-row">
      <input type="email" id="emailInput" placeholder="Votre adresse email" aria-label="Adresse email" required>
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Me prévenir →</button>
    </div>
    <p class="form-note" id="formNote">Une notification à l'ouverture. Rien d'autre.</p>
  </form>
  <p class="confirm" id="confirmMsg">Merci ! Nous vous écrirons depuis Yogyakarta dès l'ouverture.</p>

  <div class="socials">
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jamujava" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
    <a href="mailto:contact@jamujava.com" class="social-link">Nous écrire</a>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  © 2025 JAMU Java · Boissons de Java, Indonésie
</footer>

<script>
document.getElementById('notifyForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e){
  e.preventDefault();
  const email = document.getElementById('emailInput').value;
  const subject = encodeURIComponent('Avertissez-moi à l\'ouverture — JAMU Java');
  const body = encodeURIComponent('Bonjour,\n\nMerci de m\'avertir dès l\'ouverture du site JAMU Java.\n\nMon email : ' + email);
  window.location.href = 'mailto:contact@jamujava.com?subject=' + subject + '&body=' + body;
  document.getElementById('formNote').style.display = 'none';
  document.getElementById('confirmMsg').classList.add('visible');
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
